  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Genjutsu (Phantasm)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 12</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 27 | <b>Successes:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 15 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 29</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You cast an illusion upon yourself, making yourself appear slightly taller, gain crimson eyes and making your flesh seem deathly pale. Your aura becomes a visible, fiery and chaotic red and the ground beneath you seems to shake with an unearthly power. Your voice becomes booming and deep. Enemies within 50 ft of you become @Condition[shaken]{shaken} for 2d6 rounds, ordinaries become @Condition[panicked]{panicked} instead. If a creature leaves and re-enters the aura, it must make a new save. Allies within 50 ft of you instead gain a +1 morale bonus to attack rolls and saves. Enemies that correctly identify the technique or were warned about its effects gain a +8 bonus to saves to resist it.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
